data.description: Location!  simply the best.  Minutes from restaurants, shopping and the beach! Down the street from the golf course, restaurants ,town center and spa. Plenty of biking and walking trails and the house as so many upgrades.  Including, lighting, cabinets, a courtyard, granite counters, tile in all living areas, high end SS appliances.  Membership to golf and swim clubs is optional.  This property is Venetian Bay at it's best!
